In actuality MetaGame is a DAO looking for solutions. We try not to think too much about who is responsible for the mess we find ourselves in because when you zoom far enough out it's easy to see that no one group or one industry is creating the issues we face globally. It may simply be that local people focusing on local needs is not the best outcome for the global population. Instead we are choosing to build something that forges a new path into uncharted territory, with untested mechanisms, and a high risk of failure. \
